author: Inside Edition
description: The oldest working National Park Service Ranger has died. Betty Reid Soskin died at her home in Richmond, California, surrounded by loved ones, according to her Facebook page. Reid Soskin started working for the National Park Service when she was 85 years old. She retired in 2022 at the age of 100. She was posted at the Rosie the Riveter WWII Home Front National Historic Park. Inside Edition Digital’s Mara Montalbano has more.
title: Oldest National Park Service Ranger, Betty Reid Soskin, Dies at 104

author: Inside Edition
description: Rapper Nicki Minaj called JD Vance an "assassin" in a conversation with Erika Kirk, whose husband was assassination four months ago. Minaj realized her blunder and looked mortified, but Erika Kirk brushed it off. It was a wild moment in the bizarre gathering at the Turning Point USA Conference. Meanwhile, Michael Jackson's family is blasting the Trump administration Monday for linking the pop star to Jeffrey Epstein.
title: Nicki Minaj Calls JD Vance 'Assassin' In Conversation With Erika Kirk

author: Inside Edition
description: Carissa Gibbs was dumped by her fiance nine weeks before they were supposed to walk down the aisle. She already paid for the wedding dress, the venue, and the cake. So, Gibbs ate the cake, and her best friend came over for emotional support. The 24-year-old nurse says she posted the video on TikTok to show other women that there can be love after loss. Now, Gibbs found another fella and they are engaged.
title: Bride Dumped 9 Weeks Before Wedding Shows There Can Be Love After Loss

author: Inside Edition
description: An accused Walmart shoplifter was sitting on a bench with his female companion, who was also accused of shoplifting, when suddenly, the man grabbed a gun. The Walmart manager wrestled the weapon out of his hands as the police officer joined in. The suspect has been identified as 21-year-old Shane Newman. He already has an active warrant out for his arrest. Police say Newman's gun jammed, but the suspect's family says the shooting might have been an attempt at suicide by cop.
title: Bodycam Video Shows Suspected Shoplifter Pulling Out Gun

author: Inside Edition
description: After a dog fell through an icy lake, a brave officer set out on a rescue mission. It happened in Sparta, New Jersey. Officials say a patrolman certified in ice rescue, suited up and went out on Lake Mohawk to get the wayward animal. While he set out on the ice alone, he was tethered to land by fellow officers. Inside Edition Digital’s Mara Montalbano has more.
title: Dog Falls Through Icy Lake, Gets Rescued By Brave Police Officer

author: Inside Edition
description: Dr. Kehinde Idowu was in the right place to assist when John Nimmo crashed his car after a heart attack while driving in Atlanta, Georgia.
title: Doctor Saves Man Who Had Heart Attack While Driving #shorts

author: Inside Edition
description: When a barn went up in flames with animals trapped inside, county singer and TikTok star Tayler Holder tried to kick through the fence to save them.
title: Hero Country Star Saves Animals From Burning Barn #shorts
